## 5. Project Outcomes

- **Time saved:** WBR generation reduced from ~3-4 hours of manual work to a single conversation (~15 minutes including model reconnection and file generation)
- **Consistency:** All outputs derived from the same live Power BI models used by the business — no divergence from source
- **Repeatability:** Any team member can regenerate the WBR by pasting `wbr_prompt_dsr.md` and asking Claude to update — no technical knowledge required
- **Auditability:** Every query, filter, and business rule is documented in `wbr_memory_dsr.md` — complete traceability of what the numbers mean and where they come from
- **Extensibility:** The knowledge file structure and query patterns can be extended to cover additional metrics, brands, or geographies with minimal incremental effort

